{"tid":800233,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【騰訊又中槍】教育部通知　限制青年使用網絡遊戲時間","createTime":"2018-08-30T16:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T16:40:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2244472115f658e865b05f725a2b7f8c9281e5db","tid":800233,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"昨晚教育部等八部門關於印發《綜合防控兒童青少年近視實施方案》通知，其中國家新聞出版署將對網路遊戲實施總量調控，控制新增網路遊戲上網運營數量，探索符合國情的適齡提示制度，採取措施限制未成年人使用時間。<br />\n騰訊（700）在美國預託證券ADR暫折算報344.4元，較港周四收市價357.4元，跌13元或3.6%。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535646552_9521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535646552_9521.jpg&h=bfe8a120&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e2e6a161bfbc59be797e0473f4a6c4015668c9d","tid":800233,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58627347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58627347&d=SnJ3DapagYs6fShdi%2BcBewdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ba43a09e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58627347&h=6c9d2cff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58627347</a>"}]}